    %% This diagram illustrates Snowflake's native CDC (Change Data Capture)
    %% implementation using Streams and Tasks for incremental data processing.
    %%
    %% Key Concepts:
    %% - Streams: Track changes (INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE) on tables
    %% - Tasks: Serverless scheduled jobs with DAG dependencies
    %% - Medallion Architecture: Bronze → Silver → Gold
    %% - Incremental Processing: Process only changed data (efficient)
