        LoadProcess["⬇️ Data Loading<br/>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━<br/>COPY INTO bronze_orders<br/>FROM @external_stage<br/>FILE_FORMAT = csv<br/>ON_ERROR = 'CONTINUE';<br/><br/>Frequency: Every 5 min<br/>Volume: ~10K rows/batch"]

